(8, 112, ' Why Choose BIT. Consulting?', 'why-choose-bit-consulting', '<p>Welcome to our promotional page! We are an IT consulting firm ready to assist you in addressing various information technology challenges that you may face.</p>\r\n<p>We understand the importance of information technology in running your business or job. Therefore, we provide various IT consulting services to help you improve efficiency, productivity, and business security.</p>\r\n<p>Here are some of the IT consulting services we offer:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>System security analysis: We will conduct a security analysis of your system to identify vulnerabilities and provide the appropriate solutions to strengthen your system.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>System implementation: We will assist you in implementing the right information technology system to meet your business needs.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Application development consultation: We will assist you in developing applications that suit your business needs.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Data management consultation: We will assist you in organizing, managing, and utilizing your data effectively to improve your business decisions.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Cloud computing consultation: We will assist you in utilizing cloud computing to improve your business\'s flexibility and scalability.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>We have a well-trained and experienced IT consulting team. We will work with you to understand your business needs and provide the right solutions to address your information technology challenges.</p>\r\n<p>Do not hesitate to contact us for IT consulting services. We are ready to assist you in improving your business performance with better information technology!</p>', '', 1, 8, '2023-05-06 14:37:15', 161, '', '2023-05-07 13:57:33', 161, NULL, NULL, '2023-05-06 14:37:36', NULL, '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":\"\",\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":\"\",\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":\"\",\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\",\"helix_ultimate_image\":\"images\\/2023\\/05\\/07\\/IOT.jpg\",\"helix_ultimate_image_alt_txt\":\"\",\"helix_ultimate_article_format\":\"standard\",\"helix_ultimate_audio\":\"\",\"helix_ultimate_gallery\":\"\",\"helix_ultimate_video\":\"\"}', 8, 0, '', '', 1, 0, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\"}', 1, '*', ''),
(9, 113, 'Cloud Solutions', 'cloud-solutions', '<div id=\"comp-j82zpp8g\" class=\"hFQZVn comp-j82zpp8g\">\r\n<div class=\"\" data-mesh-id=\"comp-j82zpp8ginlineContent\" data-testid=\"inline-content\">\r\n<div data-mesh-id=\"comp-j82zpp8ginlineContent-gridContainer\" data-testid=\"mesh-container-content\">\r\n<div id=\"comp-j82zpp8i\" class=\"hFQZVn comp-j82zpp8i\" data-angle=\"0\" data-angle-style-location=\"style\" data-screen-in-hide=\"done\">\r\n<div class=\"\" data-mesh-id=\"comp-j82zpp8iinlineContent\" data-testid=\"inline-content\">\r\n<div data-mesh-id=\"comp-j82zpp8iinlineContent-gridContainer\" data-testid=\"mesh-container-content\">\r\n<div id=\"comp-j82zpp8j\" class=\"BaOVQ8 tz5f0K comp-j82zpp8j wixui-rich-text\" data-testid=\"richTextElement\">\r\n<p>Cloud solutions refer to the delivery of computing services, including software, storage, and processing power, over the internet. Cloud solutions allow businesses and individuals to access computing resources on-demand, without the need for a physical on-premises infrastructure. This can help reduce the cost and complexity of IT management, while also increasing scalability and flexibility.</p>\r\n', '\r\n<p>There are several types of cloud solutions available, including public, private, and hybrid clouds. Public clouds are offered by third-party providers and are accessible to anyone over the internet. Private clouds, on the other hand, are dedicated to a single organization and are not accessible to the public. Hybrid clouds combine elements of both public and private clouds, allowing organizations to leverage the benefits of both.</p>\r\n<p>Cloud solutions can be used for a variety of purposes, including data storage and backup, software development and testing, application hosting, and data analysis. Cloud computing also enables remote working and collaboration, as users can access shared resources and work together on projects from anywhere with an internet connection.</p>\r\n<p>Some of the most popular cloud solution providers include Amazon Web Services (AWS), Microsoft Azure, Google Cloud, and IBM Cloud. These providers offer a wide range of cloud services, including computing, storage, networking, security, and analytics, among others.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 1, 9, '2023-05-06 14:41:57', 161, '', '2023-05-07 05:58:16', 161, 161, '2023-05-07 09:13:04', '2023-05-06 14:41:57', NULL, '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":\"\",\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":\"\",\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":\"\",\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\",\"helix_ultimate_image\":\"\",\"helix_ultimate_image_alt_txt\":\"\",\"helix_ultimate_article_format\":\"standard\",\"helix_ultimate_audio\":\"\",\"helix_ultimate_gallery\":\"\",\"helix_ultimate_video\":\"\"}', 4, 5, '', '', 1, 0, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\"}', 1, '*', ''),
(10, 114, ' Managed IT Services', 'managed-it-services', '<div id=\"comp-j82zugna1\" class=\"hFQZVn comp-j82zugna1\">\r\n<div class=\"\" data-mesh-id=\"comp-j82zugna1inlineContent\" data-testid=\"inline-content\">\r\n<div data-mesh-id=\"comp-j82zugna1inlineContent-gridContainer\" data-testid=\"mesh-container-content\">\r\n<div id=\"comp-j82zugrw\" class=\"hFQZVn comp-j82zugrw\" data-angle=\"0\" data-angle-style-location=\"style\" data-screen-in-hide=\"done\">\r\n<div class=\"\" data-mesh-id=\"comp-j82zugrwinlineContent\" data-testid=\"inline-content\">\r\n<div data-mesh-id=\"comp-j82zugrwinlineContent-gridContainer\" data-testid=\"mesh-container-content\">\r\n<div id=\"comp-j82zugry\" class=\"BaOVQ8 tz5f0K comp-j82zugry wixui-rich-text\" data-testid=\"richTextElement\">\r\n<p>Managed IT services refer to the outsourcing of various IT functions to a third-party provider who assumes responsibility for the ongoing monitoring, maintenance, and management of a company\'s IT infrastructure.</p>\r\n', '\r\n<p>These services typically include tasks such as network management, data backup and recovery, software patching and updates, cybersecurity management, and help desk support. By outsourcing these functions, companies can focus on their core business operations while leaving the technical aspects of their IT infrastructure to experienced professionals.</p>\r\n<p>Managed IT services are particularly useful for small and medium-sized businesses that may not have the resources to hire a full-time IT staff. By partnering with a managed service provider (MSP), these companies can gain access to the latest technologies and IT expertise without having to bear the costs of hiring, training, and retaining an in-house team.</p>\r\n<p>MSPs typically offer their services on a subscription basis, providing a predictable monthly cost that includes all of the services required to keep a company\'s IT infrastructure running smoothly. This model enables companies to better manage their IT budgets and plan for future growth, knowing that their technology needs are being handled by a team of experts.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 1, 9, '2023-05-06 14:44:36', 161, '', '2023-05-07 06:05:37', 161, NULL, NULL, '2023-05-06 14:44:36', NULL, '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":\"\",\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":\"\",\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":\"\",\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\",\"helix_ultimate_image\":\"\",\"helix_ultimate_image_alt_txt\":\"\",\"helix_ultimate_article_format\":\"standard\",\"helix_ultimate_audio\":\"\",\"helix_ultimate_gallery\":\"\",\"helix_ultimate_video\":\"\"}', 5, 3, '', '', 1, 0, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\"}', 1, '*', ''),
(11, 115, ' Disaster Recovery', 'disaster-recovery', '<div id=\"comp-j82zyvsk\" class=\"hFQZVn comp-j82zyvsk\">\r\n<div class=\"\" data-mesh-id=\"comp-j82zyvskinlineContent\" data-testid=\"inline-content\">\r\n<div data-mesh-id=\"comp-j82zyvskinlineContent-gridContainer\" data-testid=\"mesh-container-content\">\r\n<div id=\"comp-j82zyvt9\" class=\"hFQZVn comp-j82zyvt9\" data-angle=\"0\" data-angle-style-location=\"style\" data-screen-in-hide=\"done\">\r\n<div class=\"\" data-mesh-id=\"comp-j82zyvt9inlineContent\" data-testid=\"inline-content\">\r\n<div data-mesh-id=\"comp-j82zyvt9inlineContent-gridContainer\" data-testid=\"mesh-container-content\">\r\n<div id=\"comp-j82zyvtb\" class=\"BaOVQ8 tz5f0K comp-j82zyvtb wixui-rich-text\" data-testid=\"richTextElement\">\r\n<p>Disaster recovery refers to the process of restoring systems, data, and applications after a disruptive event such as a natural disaster, cyber attack, or hardware failure. The goal of disaster recovery is to minimize the impact of the disaster on business operations, prevent data loss, and ensure the continuity of critical business functions.</p>\r\n', '\r\n<p>Disaster recovery typically involves several steps, including:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Disaster response: The initial response to the disaster involves assessing the damage, ensuring employee safety, and implementing emergency measures to prevent further damage.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Business continuity planning: This involves identifying critical business functions and developing plans to ensure that these functions can continue in the event of a disaster. This may include establishing alternate work sites, securing backup systems and data, and identifying key personnel.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Disaster recovery planning: This involves developing a plan to restore systems, data, and applications to their pre-disaster state. This may involve restoring data from backups, repairing or replacing damaged hardware, and testing systems to ensure they are functioning properly.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Testing and maintenance: It\'s important to regularly test and maintain disaster recovery plans to ensure they remain effective and up-to-date. This includes conducting regular drills and simulations to identify areas that need improvement and updating plans as necessary.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>Overall, a well-designed disaster recovery plan is essential for any organization that relies on technology to conduct business. By taking proactive steps to prepare for disasters, organizations can minimize the impact of disruptions and ensure the continuity of critical business functions.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 1, 9, '2023-05-06 14:47:27', 161, '', '2023-05-07 06:11:52', 161, NULL, NULL, '2023-05-06 14:47:27', NULL, '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":\"\",\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":\"\",\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":\"\",\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\",\"helix_ultimate_image\":\"\",\"helix_ultimate_image_alt_txt\":\"\",\"helix_ultimate_article_format\":\"standard\",\"helix_u