(41, 'index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=13', 'index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=13:network-solutions&catid=9', ' Network Solutions', ' Network Solutions is a technology company that provides domain name registration, website hosting, website design, and online marketing services to individuals and businesses. The company was founded in 1979 and was one of the first domain registrars on the internet. In addition to domain registration and hosting services, Network Solutions also offers a variety of website design and marketing tools to help businesses establish and grow their online presence. Some of these tools include website templates, website builder software, and search engine optimization (SEO) services. Network Solutions is now a subsidiary of Web.com, which is a publicly traded company that provides a range of online marketing services to small businesses. Network Solutions has been a prominent player in the domain name industry for many years. In the early days of the internet, Network Solutions held a monopoly on domain name registration and was the only organization authorized to register domain names. However, with the opening up of the market, other domain registrars have emerged and the competition has increased. Today, Network Solutions still offers domain registration services, but it also provides a range of other services aimed at helping businesses establish and maintain an online presence. These services include web hosting, website design and development, e-commerce solutions, email marketing, and online advertising. Network Solutions has a wide customer base that includes small businesses, large corporations, and individual website owners. The company offers a range of pricing options, from affordable packages for small businesses to more comprehensive plans for larger organizations. Overall, Network Solutions is a well-established and reputable company in the online services industry, and it continues to evolve and expand its offerings to meet the changing needs of its customers. ', '2023-05-07 06:24:10', '2ed268153a7dba200101ae7fbd49cab9', 1, 1, 1, '*', '2023-05-06 14:51:39', NULL, '2023-05-06 14:51:39', NULL, 0, 0, 3, ),
(42, 'index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=14', 'index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=14:support-consulting&catid=9', ' Support Consulting', ' Support consulting is a type of professional service that provides expert guidance and support to businesses or organizations in a particular field. The goal of support consulting is to help companies improve their performance, achieve their goals, and solve specific problems or challenges they are facing. ', '2023-05-07 06:28:14', 'c618f305b307e9a783b4b601d6ca785d', 1, 1, 1, '*', '2023-05-06 14:53:26', NULL, '2023-05-06 14:53:26', NULL, 0, 0, 3, ),
