(38, 'com_content.article.13', '', '2023-05-07 06:24:10', 161, 4591, 'b978c3e15d6c060630db551a1ef3c834c3934cc1', '{\"id\":\"13\",\"asset_id\":117,\"title\":\" Network Solutions\",\"alias\":\"network-solutions\",\"introtext\":\"<div id=\\\"comp-j83083h6\\\" class=\\\"hFQZVn comp-j83083h6\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"\\\" data-mesh-id=\\\"comp-j83083h6inlineContent\\\" data-testid=\\\"inline-content\\\">\\r\\n<div data-mesh-id=\\\"comp-j83083h6inlineContent-gridContainer\\\" data-testid=\\\"mesh-container-content\\\">\\r\\n<div id=\\\"comp-j83083hx\\\" class=\\\"hFQZVn comp-j83083hx\\\" data-angle=\\\"0\\\" data-angle-style-location=\\\"style\\\" data-screen-in-hide=\\\"done\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"\\\" data-mesh-id=\\\"comp-j83083hxinlineContent\\\" data-testid=\\\"inline-content\\\">\\r\\n<div data-mesh-id=\\\"comp-j83083hxinlineContent-gridContainer\\\" data-testid=\\\"mesh-container-content\\\">\\r\\n<div id=\\\"comp-j83083i0\\\" class=\\\"BaOVQ8 tz5f0K comp-j83083i0 wixui-rich-text\\\" data-testid=\\\"richTextElement\\\">\\r\\n<p>Network Solutions is a technology company that provides domain name registration, website hosting, website design, and online marketing services to individuals and businesses. The company was founded in 1979 and was one of the first domain registrars on the internet.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>In addition to domain registration and hosting services, Network Solutions also offers a variety of website design and marketing tools to help businesses establish and grow their online presence. Some of these tools include website templates, website builder software, and search engine optimization (SEO) services.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Network Solutions is now a subsidiary of Web.com, which is a publicly traded company that provides a range of online marketing services to small businesses.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Network Solutions has been a prominent player in the domain name industry for many years. In the early days of the internet, Network Solutions held a monopoly on domain name registration and was the only organization authorized to register domain names. However, with the opening up of the market, other domain registrars have emerged and the competition has increased.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Today, Network Solutions still offers domain registration services, but it also provides a range of other services aimed at helping businesses establish and maintain an online presence. These services include web hosting, website design and development, e-commerce solutions, email marketing, and online advertising.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Network Solutions has a wide customer base that includes small businesses, large corporations, and individual website owners. The company offers a range of pricing options, from affordable packages for small businesses to more comprehensive plans for larger organizations.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Overall, Network Solutions is a well-established and reputable company in the online services industry, and it continues to evolve and expand its offerings to meet the changing needs of its customers.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":9,\"created\":\"2023-05-06 14:51:39\",\"created_by\":\"161\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2023-05-07 06:24:10\",\"modified_by\":161,\"checked_out\":161,\"checked_out_time\":\"2023-05-07 06:16:33\",\"publish_up\":\"2023-05-06 14:51:39\",\"publish_down\":null,\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_image\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_image_alt_txt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_article_format\\\":\\\"standard\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_audio\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_gallery\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_video\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":3,\"ordering\":1,\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":1,\"hits\":0,\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"1\",\"language\":\"*\",\"note\":\"\"}', 0),
(39, 'com_content.article.14', '', '2023-05-07 06:28:14', 161, 3886, '9f7a2ec105496b5db9c4b4897cb0f96b51c84bc1', '{\"id\":\"14\",\"asset_id\":118,\"title\":\" Support Consulting\",\"alias\":\"support-consulting\",\"introtext\":\"<div id=\\\"comp-j830bu6q\\\" class=\\\"hFQZVn comp-j830bu6q\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"\\\" data-mesh-id=\\\"comp-j830bu6qinlineContent\\\" data-testid=\\\"inline-content\\\">\\r\\n<div data-mesh-id=\\\"comp-j830bu6qinlineContent-gridContainer\\\" data-testid=\\\"mesh-container-content\\\">\\r\\n<div id=\\\"comp-j830bu6r\\\" class=\\\"hFQZVn comp-j830bu6r\\\" data-angle=\\\"0\\\" data-angle-style-location=\\\"style\\\" data-screen-in-hide=\\\"done\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"\\\" data-mesh-id=\\\"comp-j830bu6rinlineContent\\\" data-testid=\\\"inline-content\\\">\\r\\n<div data-mesh-id=\\\"comp-j830bu6rinlineContent-gridContainer\\\" data-testid=\\\"mesh-container-content\\\">\\r\\n<div id=\\\"comp-j830bu6t\\\" class=\\\"BaOVQ8 tz5f0K comp-j830bu6t wixui-rich-text\\\" data-testid=\\\"richTextElement\\\">\\r\\n<p>Support consulting is a type of professional service that provides expert guidance and support to businesses or organizations in a particular field. The goal of support consulting is to help companies improve their performance, achieve their goals, and solve specific problems or challenges they are facing.<\\/p>\\r\\n\",\"fulltext\":\"\\r\\n<p>Support consultants work closely with clients to understand their needs, identify opportunities for improvement, and develop customized strategies and solutions to help them achieve their objectives. They provide advice, guidance, and hands-on support, drawing on their expertise and knowledge of industry best practices.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Some common areas of support consulting include information technology, marketing and branding, human resources, financial management, and operations management. Support consultants may specialize in one or more of these areas, depending on their skills and experience.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Overall, support consulting is about providing companies with the tools, resources, and knowledge they need to succeed and thrive in a competitive business environment. By working with support consultants, companies can improve their performance, reduce costs, increase efficiency, and achieve their goals more effectively.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":9,\"created\":\"2023-05-06 14:53:26\",\"created_by\":\"161\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2023-05-07 06:28:14\",\"modified_by\":161,\"checked_out\":161,\"checked_out_time\":\"2023-05-07 06:24:24\",\"publish_up\":\"2023-05-06 14:53:26\",\"publish_down\":null,\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_image\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_image_alt_txt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_article_format\\\":\\\"standard\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_audio\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_gallery\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_video\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":3,\"ordering\":0,\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":1,\"hits\":0,\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"1\",\"language\":\"*\",\"note\":\"\"}', 0);
